---
import amazonRainforest from "../../assets/generalidades/Introduction/amazon-rainforest.jpg";
import audiomoth from "../../assets/generalidades/Introduction/audiomoth.webp";
---

<div class="space-y-6">
  <!-- Header Section with Hero Image -->
  <div class="card relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image with Overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img
        src={amazonRainforest.src}
        alt="Amazonía Peruana"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-25"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900/70 to-gray-900/95"></div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <!-- Title with Icon -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
        <div class="bg-green-900/50 rounded-full p-3 mr-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">Monitoreo Acústico de Primates</h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Intro -->
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">
          La Amazonía Peruana, epicentro de biodiversidad, enfrenta presiones que amenazan sus ecosistemas y especies, incluyendo primates neotropicales. El monitoreo efectivo es crucial para la conservación.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Key Points with Icons -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-2">
        <div class="bg-gray-900/70 p-3 rounded-lg flex items-start">
          <div class="bg-green-900/50 rounded-full p-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-green-300">Biodiversidad</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Protección de ecosistemas únicos y especies de primates neotropicales</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-900/70 p-3 rounded-lg flex items-start">
          <div class="bg-green-900/50 rounded-full p-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-green-300">Monitoreo</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Evaluación del impacto humano y guía de estrategias de conservación</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-900/70 p-3 rounded-lg flex items-start">
          <div class="bg-green-900/50 rounded-full p-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 5v2m0 4v2m0 4v2M5 5a2 2 0 00-2 2v3a2 2 0 110 4v3a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-3a2 2 0 110-4V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-green-300">Desafíos</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Análisis de grandes volúmenes de datos acústicos</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PAM Section with device image -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
      <div class="bg-green-900/50 rounded-full p-2 mr-3">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-400">Monitoreo Acústico Pasivo (PAM)</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- AudioMoth Device -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 shadow-md">
          <img
            src={audiomoth.src}
            alt="Dispositivo AudioMoth"
            class="w-full h-auto max-h-40 object-contain mx-auto"
          />
          <p class="text-xs text-center text-gray-400 mt-2">Dispositivo AudioMoth</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PAM Benefits -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 flex flex-col">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-3 rounded-lg flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-green-900/50 rounded-full p-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-xs font-medium text-green-300">No invasivo</h5>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Ideal para especies elusivas</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-3 rounded-lg flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-green-900/50 rounded-full p-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-xs font-medium text-green-300">Monitoreo continuo</h5>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">24/7 con mínima presencia humana</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-3 rounded-lg flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-green-900/50 rounded-full p-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-xs font-medium text-green-300">Bajo costo</h5>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Sensores económicos (AudioMoths)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-3 rounded-lg flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-green-900/50 rounded-full p-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-xs font-medium text-green-300">Grandes datos</h5>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Recolección de volúmenes masivos</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .card {
    background-color: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(55, 65, 81, 0.6);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15);
  }
</style>
